Splunk
======
Splunk takes data of any report and generate rich reports, to investigate,alert,build dash boards etc.

Splunk is an IT operations tool that consumes machine-data in real time. Most of BI(Business Intelligence) tools do not consume & analyse data in real time.

Deployments
===========
Single Deployment 
Distributed 
Cloud

Any deployment model consists of Data input, Parsing & INdexing , Searching.